{{Infobox Character |name = Clad |image = XC3 Clad Icon.png |species = |age = 8th term |gender = Male |haircolor = |eyecolor = |affiliation = [[Colony 11]] |voiceactorjp = |voiceactoreng = |appearances = {{XC3}} }} '''Clad''' is a NPC in {{XC3}}. He can be found in Colony 11.
== Overview == Clad is a lieutenant of [[Colony 11]] and captain of its defense squad. [[Rattlejack]] and [[Knoquehardt]] are his subordinates. He is known to be silent most of the time, and has a hard time of feeling any physical sensation, leading him to the battlefield in search of something that can bring pain, in order to at least feel something. He is also one of Three Ravens, alongside his fellow lieutenants [[Easel]] and [[Zoren]].
== Affinity == * [[Ashera]] * [[Easel]] * [[Zoren]] * [[Rattlejack]] * [[Knoquehardt]] {{clr}}
