'''Class Mastery Shop Blue''' is a [[Shop (XC3)|DLC Shop]] in {{XC3}}. It can be found in the [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]], available as part of the [[Challenge Battle Mode]] of the [[Xenoblade Chronicles 3#Expansion%20Pass|Expansion Pass]], and it is run by [[Archsage's Aide, Blue]]. Blue [[Noponstone]]s can be traded here in exchange for unlocking a [[Class (XC3)|class]] for a character.
{{clr}}

