{{Infobox location |name = Clifftop Ferronis Hulk |image = Clifftop Ferronis Hulk.jpg |caption = Clifftop Ferronis Hulk |type = [[Rest Spot (XC3)|Rest Spot]] |located = [[Urayan Trail]] |inhabitants = |weather = |connects to = |music = }} '''Clifftop Ferronis Hulk''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|崖上の朽ちた鉄巨神}}, ''Gaijō no Kuchita Tetsukyoshin'') is a [[Rest Spot (XC3)|Rest Spot]] in {{XC3}}. It is located on the [[Urayan Trail]] in the [[Pentelas Region]]. This [[Ferronis Hulk]] is rebooted by completing ''[[The Clifftop Hulk]]''. {{clr}}
