{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |category = Unique Monster |name = Clinging Azreel |image = XC3 Clinging Azreel.png |caption = Clinging Azreel |type = [[Flak]] |level = 69 |area = [[Origin Interior]] ([[Central Defense]]) |spawntime = Anytime |respawn = Yes |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 3,652 |cp = 475 |sp = 5 |gold = 1,380 |hp = 2,504,600 |strength = 2,091 |healing = 395 |dexterity = 304 |agility = 250 |physdef = 10% |ethdef = -10% |critrate = 12% |guardrate = 0% }} '''Clinging Azreel''' is a [[Unique Monster (XC3)|Unique Monster]] in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Flak]] family, and can be found at level 69 at the [[Central Defense]] in the [[Origin Interior]]. The [[Elimination Beam]] [[Battle Arts (XC3)|Art]] can be earned by the [[Soulhacker]] [[Class (XC3)|class]] by defeating it.
