{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Codon Quardun |image = Codon Quardun.jpg |caption = Codon Quardun |category = Minor Enemy |type = [[Quardun]] |level = 28-29 |area = [[Great Cotte Falls]] |spawntime = Anytime |respawn = Yes |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = }} '''Codon Quarduns''' are Minor Enemies in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. They are members of the [[Quardun]] family, and can be found at levels 28-29 directly north of the [[Titan Rock Camp]] at [[Great Cotte Falls]]. They can drop [[Quardun Fang]], one of which is required at Rare quality to craft [[Analyze Weakness|Analyze Weakness IV]], and [[Quardun Shell]], one of which is required at Rare quality to craft [[Steel Protection|Steel Protection IV]], without the use of [[Nopon Coin (Gold)|Gold Nopon Coins]]. {{clr}}
